title: Grateful Dead Live at Oakland Auditorium Arena on 1980-12-28
description:
Set 1

Mississippi Half Step-> Franklin's Tower, Me & My Uncle-> Big River, Bird Song, Little Red Rooster, Althea, Jack Straw

Set 2

Don't Ease Me In, Lost Sailor-> Saint Of Circumstance-> Terrapin Station-> Drums-> The Other One-> Stella Blue-> Sugar Magnolia, E: Casey Jones

reviews.review_text: Pure listen... This is such a nice Grateful Dead concert. Start to finish. I have listened to it so many times over the years and here I am, September 2024, listening to it again. Great feel and vibe to this show. Enjoy...
